title: Documents about members of Medellín cartel (Drug Enforcement Administration)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

All records relating to, mentioning or describing JESUS GALINDO PEREZ and FRANK LINO-DIAZ, members of Medellín Cartel, that lived in USA and are arrested in Brazil, in 80's. 

To assist in identifying records, the following is known of GALINDO PEREZ:
Nationality: Colombian
Date of Birth: 10/01/1950

To assist in identifying records, the following is known of FRANK LINO-DIAZ:
Nationality: Cuban / American
Date of Birth: 09/23/1950

Please return a result for a query of Drugs Enforcement Administration (DEA) and Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) using each aforementioned subject's name and (where necessary) accompanying nationality or dates of birth.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Allan Abreu
